data.description: Crave solitude with room to breathe? Dive into this 3BR, 1.75BA sanctuary on a secure 1.25-acre expansive property. Key perks? RV utilities with sewage, a spacious 26x26 workshop w/new electrical & lighting, an inviting firepit, and a large deck, all within a 1510 sqft efficiently designed home. Upgrades? A 2020-installed roof and washer/dryer, 2019 water heater, revamped kitchen & baths, and a welcoming woodstove.  Enjoy the flowing design connecting kitchen, dining, and living areas, highlighted by French doors leading to deck. The primary suite is a haven w/bay window, generous walk-in closet and updated bath. For the outdoorsy? The sound and trails of the PNW are just a stone's throw away.
